{"type":"text","timestamp":1775847303753,"sessionID":"ses_28741be16ffex4k31WreDJMoNA","part":{"id":"prt_d78bf645c0018PCZtg0pwC3ToX","messageID":"msg_d78bf42600012TDlZ4WcqQJ2Dx","sessionID":"ses_28741be16ffex4k31WreDJMoNA","type":"text","text":"I've added AR-008 (Sandbox GC 定时清理机制) to the proposal.md file. The proposal includes a comprehensive plan for implementing a scheduled garbage collection mechanism for Sandbox resources, covering:\n\n- Purpose: Clean up expired, orphaned, or inactive resources\n- Module: `pkg/workloadmanager` in Go 1.24\n- Configuration options (interval, grace periods, dry-run mode)\n- Testing strategy (unit, integration, performance tests)\n- Security and performance considerations\n- Alternatives considered and rejected","time":{"start":1775847303751,"end":1775847303751}}}
